This is a '''list of Cascade volcanoes''', i.e. [[volcano]]es formed as a result of subduction along the [[Cascadia subduction zone]] in the [[Pacific Northwest]] of North America. The volcanoes are listed from north to south, by province or state: [[British Columbia]], [[Washington (state)|Washington]], [[Oregon]], and [[California]].

{{GeoGroup}}

